body:
Perhaps you have an older version of TensorFlow, it's been renamed to axis in 0.12
```
>>> import tensorflow as tf
>>> tf.__version__
'0.12.1'
>>> tf.expand_dims([1], axis=1)
<tf.Tensor 'ExpandDims:0' shape=(1, 1) dtype=int32>

```
